00:01:39.915 --> 00:01:45.325
When you hear the name “James Bond”, a certain image probably comes to mind.

00:01:46.205 --> 00:01:52.115
For many it might be a man in a smart tuxedo, a black dinner jacket.

00:01:52.715 --> 00:01:57.865
He might be sitting at a card table, he might be holding a gun, he might

